{"tid":1001504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"又過了一年","createTime":"2019-01-30T08:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T08:34:22.000Z","uid":36961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea869169ecd33c229fdab7f12171d8ad8fe2ff16","tid":1001504,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"每年呢個時候 都會手多執間房<br />\n明明知 執完可能都仲係咁亂<br />\n但都想做番次掃除<br />\n點知睇番啲野 先知道 哦原來時間過得咁快<br />\n小學個本紀念冊 中學同學寫既聖誕卡<br />\nOcamp啲人寫既龜背<br />\n你第一個女朋友送比你既禮物 你第一次整禮物比人整剩既既材料 傷得你最深既人 你傷得最深既人<br />\n一啲已經唔存在唔再同你人生有交集既人同埋事<br />\n雖然係咁 但係你都好唔捨得咁將佢地扔左佢<br />\n永遠都留番一個位擺呢堆野 明知呢啲野係有幾無用 你都唔會扔佢<br />\n可能直到有一日 你會扔走佢地 但唔係依一刻<br />\n因為 你仲未放低到呢啲記憶 或者係自己念舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位農曆新年快樂"},{"pid":"b97fff5e78ab0ba3519f131b958048ebf907d645","tid":1001504,"uid":213463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562a15274e45308116788b3512246c768912c4b1","tid":1001504,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"你再repost"},{"pid":"87dcfdadd1857dde6bef30046f177da105057efb","tid":1001504,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"1左"},{"pid":"a7bb6f8379ac77713a486b554d75967da9f5edd3","tid":1001504,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b97fff5e78ab0ba3519f131b958048ebf907d645","tid":1001504,"uid":213463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7430ea996e5d0adc9e306d00e22f04b2fb5876","tid":1001504,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562a15274e45308116788b3512246c768912c4b1","tid":1